Marjorie Monaghan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Monaghan 0 Marjorie Monaghan is a California-born American actress. Raised in Cincinnati, Ohio, she is best known for her portrayal in 1997 and 1998 of Theresa Halloran (aka 'Number One', leader of the Mars Resistance) in the television series Babylon 5.
